data.description:
***FULL IMPACT SLIDERS! This charming townhome in the Village of Sandalwood Lakes offers convenient access to major highways, shopping, dining, and the Palm Beach International Airport. As you enter through the lovely, fenced courtyard, you'll step into a spacious living room connected to a well-equipped kitchen and dining area. Downstairs, you'll find a full washer and dryer along with a convenient half bath. Upstairs, there are two primary suites, both with walk-in closets and sliders that provide picturesque views of the courtyard.  Residents can enjoy three community pools, picnic areas, tennis, and pickleball, making it an ideal place for affordable and enjoyable living. Don't miss the opportunity to make this townhome your new home! ***Property may qualify for Easy Path Financing with only 3% down. 
**Patio table, chairs, large umbrella, and storage bin are included***
